title: Game Character Female Elf Voice Pack
description: It’s a valuable collection of versatile female voice-over sound files created for MMO, RPG, fantasy, medieval games & trailers.
longDescription:
Click HERE for SoundCloud Demo!

Click HERE for YouTube Demo!


All Lightly Edited & Dry Recordings

AAA Game Character Female Elf voiceover sound library provides you with more than 590+ immersive, game-ready voice-over sound effects, vocalizations, battle cries, custom character-specific dialogue lines, stock non-player character dialogue lines, and everything needed to create compelling scenes, unique characters, and outstanding gameplay audio experiences.


Full Voice Control & Delivery

Each phrase, line, & vocalization comes with 1-3 variations giving full control to orchestrate the delivery & tone. The Female Elf’s voice profile is soft-spoken, quiet, innocent with yet strong with an edge. She is perfect for a hero, queen, wealthy townspeople, warrior princess, NPC, or any fantasy game characters. Her voice is ready for your game as is and is also provided in clean audio format for further processing with effects as desired.


Optimum Quality

AAA Game Character Female Elf voiceover sound effects collections is not only packed with high-quality voice recordings, but it also includes thought-out, cohesive scripted dialogue and vocalizations to help you build dynamic fantasy, sci-fi, adventure stories, game trailers, in-game characters, and more. All it takes is a little creativity and the little elven female to inspire interactive gameplay.
technicalDetails:
Product Details:

  • 597 female voice-over audio files
  • 290.5 MB of voice samples
  • All in 44.1k/16-Bit .wav audio file format (96k/24-Bit Versions are available through ESM directly)
  • Includes Soundminer Metadata
  • AAA Game Character Voice-Over Sound Effects Library
  • Perfect for NPC, protagonist characters, medieval, fantasy games, film and movie trailers voices
  • 25 battle cries & cheers – attack, victory, retreat
  • 6 breathing – inhale, exhale
  • 4 coughing – choking, sick
  • 2 crying – heavy, happy
  • 321 immersive character-specific dialogue lines – I’m Entrusting This Task To You!
  • 8 fight vocalizations
  • 3 jumping vocalizations – medium, hard
  • 15 laughing – crazy, chuckling, insane, light, medium, explosive
  • 29 fight & pain vocalizations – grab, death, land on ground, gut hit, throw –
  • 61 stock dialogue lines – like hello, farewell, alright
  • Works with any DAW or Game Engine
  • All Royalty Free
  • RTU-OTB (ready to use out of the box)
